  "markdown": "Anyon Systems Inc. \u00b7 Montr\u00e9al \u00b7 A Canadian quantum company\n[](https://anyonsys.com/en)\n  * Company\n  * Markets\n  * [Products](https://anyonsys.com/en/products)\n  * [Technology](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology)\n  * [News](https://anyonsys.com/en/news)\n  * Careers\n  * FR\n\n\nFR[Contact](https://anyonsys.com/en/contact)\n![](https://anyonsys.com/assets/site-images/pexels-vinayak-khithani-8779756.jpg?v=cfc17f3)\n# Bringing real quantum hardware into the research and training environment.\n![Anyon superconducting quantum computer cryostat](https://anyonsys.com/assets/site-images/open-cube-harness.jpg?v=cfc17f3)\n## Quantum Hardware for Research, Training, and Discovery\nUniversities and research institutions are essential to the quantum ecosystem because they train the engineers, physicists, computer scientists, and hardware specialists needed to scale the field.\nAnyon provides superconducting quantum systems and campus strategies that help academic users move from theory to hands-on hardware engagement while building talent pipelines in device fabrication, cryogenic RF engineering, yield engineering, and process control.\n## Anyon helps universities and research institutions:\n  * Access real superconducting quantum hardware\n  * Train students and researchers on deployable systems\n  * Support quantum algorithm and hardware research\n  * Build national talent pipelines\n  * Connect academic discovery with industrial deployment\n\n\n[](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/telecom)[Explore industrial R&D](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/industrial-rd)\nExplore how Anyon can help your organization deploy, integrate, and scale quantum infrastructure.\n[Contact](https://anyonsys.com/en/contact)\n![Anyon Systems](https://anyonsys.com/assets/logo_pure-white.svg?v=cfc17f3)\nFull-stack superconducting quantum systems. Designed and built in Montr\u00e9al.\n  * [About](https://anyonsys.com/en/company/about)\n  * [News](https://anyonsys.com/en/news)\n  * [Careers](https://anyonsys.com/en/careers/jobs)\n\n\nMontr\u00e9al \u00b7 QC \u00b7 Canada\n[LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/anyon-systems-inc-/)\nMarkets\n  * [HPC centres](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/hpc)\n  * [Government](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/government)\n  * [Defence](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/defence)\n  * [Universities](https://anyonsys.com/en/markets/research)\n\n\nProducts\n  * [Qube](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#qube)\n  * [Hudson](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#hudson)\n  * [Snowflurry](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#snowflurry)\n  * [Roadmap](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#roadmap)\n\n\nTechnology\n  * [Quantum processor](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology#quantum-processor)\n  * [Cryogenic system](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology#cryogenic-system)\n  * [Control electronics](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology#control-electronics)\n  * [Software stack](https://anyonsys.com/en/technology#software-stack)\n\n\nResources\n  * [Roadmap](https://anyonsys.com/en/products#roadmap)\n\n\nHead office\nMontr\u00e9al \u00b7 Quebec\n8275 Trans Canada Route A410\nSaint-Laurent, QC H4S 0B6\nQuebec\nBromont \u00b7 Quebec\n45 Bd de l\u2019A\u00e9roport\nBromont, QC J2L 2X4\nQuebec\nSherbrooke \u00b7 Quebec\n3000 Bd de l\u2019Universit\u00e9\nSherbrooke, QC J1K 0A5\nOntario\nWaterloo \u00b7 Ontario\n295 Hagey Blvd #2\nWaterloo, ON N2L 6R5\nUnited Kingdom\nKidlington\nOxford Technology Park, Technology Dr\nKidlington OX5 1GN\nIsrael\nIsrael\nAddress coming soon\n\u00a9 2026 Anyon Systems Inc.\n[Privacy](https://anyonsys.com/en/privacy)[Support](https://anyonsys.com/en/contact)\nTop\n",
